<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以給我一點時間嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要好好想一想<delay20 />
該怎麼發洩這股怒氣才好，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />討厭，氣死人了！！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能不能先別管我，<delay20 />
暫時讓我一個人靜一靜呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經忍耐到極限了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有事找我的話，可以等一下再說嗎？<delay40 />
因為我現在完全沒那個心情！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />真是的，也太過分了吧！<delay frames="40" />
一副好像只要是我的事，
<gender3 m="他" f="她" />都知道得一清二楚的樣子！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～真討厭<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明明也是以自己的方式在享受生活，<delay20 />
為什麼要強迫我接受別人的價值觀呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
一定也有<gender3 m="他" f="她" />自己的興趣和喜好吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼就是沒辦法理解我的想法呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00">因為買東西是我的興趣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以如果有想要的東西，<delay20 />
我就會想盡量用便宜的價格買下來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />卻說什麼，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是個大人就不應該計較金錢，<delay8 />
想買什麼直接買就好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種說法我實在不能接受<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是用便宜的價錢買到好東西才高興呀！<delay40 />
再說了，我又不是沒有錢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我懂</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />是喔～</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能聽到你這麼說真是太好了！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay20 />
一定能夠理解我的心情。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想就算是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
<gender3 m="他" f="她" />在買同一樣東西時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定也會覺得買到便宜的比較開心！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起只是為了買想要的東西而去購物，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得事先決定好原則的購物方式，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更能培養一個人的生活能力。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然把東西買到手很重要，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果能夠合理地進行購物，<delay8 />　
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />獲得的喜悅一定也會更多喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，真抱歉。<delay20 />
我現在實在沒那個心情<delay20 />
和你說話好嗎！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在不想和任何人說話！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我整理好心情之前，<delay20 />
能先讓我一個人靜一靜嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay20 />正在氣頭上！<delay40 />
拜託暫時別管我，<tag a="100" b="0" /><delay8 /><endTag a="100" b="0" />
好嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你找我有什麼事嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別忘了我現在正在氣頭上！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />嗯……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />唉～<delay20 />真是的，算了算了！<delay40 />　
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看在你有反省的分上，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次我就不跟你計較了，<delay20 />
但是之後你可要多注意喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～真是的，<delay20 />居然擺出這副表情，
這樣太犯規了啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我也想早點跟你和好，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以今天的事，<delay8 />
我就當沒發生過吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
